The figure shows the static nesting of subroutines. In the stack frame of the subroutine s{=floor((10000+{a1}*1000+{b1}*100+{c1}*10+{d1})/pow(10,{e1}))} can there be a dynamic link to the frame of the subroutine s{=floor((10000+{a2}*1000+{b2}*100+{c1}*10+{d2})/pow(10,{e2}))}?


answer 0-not, 1-yes
